      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed (4.1M, 9.8M, 21.6M cells). Richardson extrapolation yields GCI of 3.1% for NIH at the worst-case operating point (6 LPM, 3500 RPM). Discretization error meets the 5% acceptance threshold."
