      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump, which is the reference geometry for this COU. Operating conditions in validation experiments (2–6 LPM, 2500–4500 RPM) fully span the CPB COU envelope. Blood analog fluid properties match clinical CPB conditions within accepted physiological range."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
