      "rationale": "CFD boundary conditions set to match reported experimental values in the FDA benchmark dataset. Inlet velocity profiles derived from fully developed pipe flow assumption consistent with experimental inlet length. Equivalency formally assessed only at MRL 3 and above per ASME V&V 40 Table 3; not required here."
